Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: APKTool fails with "brut.androlib.AndrolibException"

Solution: Update APKTool to latest version or use -r flag to skip resource decoding
Issue: JADX produces unreadable code

Solution: Try --deobf flag for obfuscated APKs or use alternative decompilers
Issue: Python script fails with encoding errors

Solution: Add encoding='utf-8', errors='ignore' when reading files
Issue: Cannot find specific vulnerability patterns

Solution: Obfuscated code may hide patterns; try searching for method signatures instead
Issue: Reports directory permission denied

Solution: Ensure directory exists and has write permissions: mkdir -p reports && chmod 755 reports
